features: HEALTHIER FOOD – Dash Tasti-Crisp Air Fryer uses AirCrisp Technology instead of oil to cook vegetables, frozen foods and more, reducing added fat by 70-80%. It’s a must-have mini kitchen appliance and the cream white air fryer looks great in any kitchen.
CERAMIC NONSTICK SURFACE – Enjoy the ceramic benefits! This ceramic air fryer has an easy-release nonstick ceramic surface that requires less oil for cooking and makes it an easy clean air fryer.

PERSONAL AIR FRYER – Whether you’re cooking healthier for one or two or want an air fryer for dorm or RV, this small size is ideal. The mini air fryer doesn’t take up much room in a kitchen or dorm but has plenty of surface area inside the ceramic basket.

CUSTOM PRESETS – Our digital air fryer includes three saved preset buttons and has a simple digital interface that allows you to choose from 200-400°F and up to 60 minutes. Also has an auto-shut off function to prevent overcooking and a cool touch handle.

FAST, HEALTHIER FOOD - Healthy food doesn’t have to take hours. Whether you’re in between classes or just short on time, with this air cooker oven, you can fry, roast, bake, crisp and much more in minutes.
body.description: Cook healthier, crispy food in a dash with Tasti-Crisp™ Ceramic Air Fryer! This versatile ceramic, electric air fryer uses AirCrisp® technology, cooking food with hot air instead of oil, reducing added fat by 70-80%. You’ll love the benefits of ceramic in the kitchen. The ceramic coated air fryer has an easy-release nonstick surface that requires less oil and makes it an easy clean air fryer.The convenient mini air fryer is sized for any kitchen, making storage easy without taking up too much room. The 2.6 qt. capacity and redesigned Crisper Basket allows for greater surface area, ensuring perfectly crisp food, every time.Whether you’re cooking healthier for one or two or want a compact, mini air fryer for your dorm room or apartment, this size is ideal. The digital air fryer oven features three saved preset buttons that allows for saving your favorite cooking settings. Plus, the easy-to-use digital interface allows for maximum control over time and temperature, from 200-400°F and up to 60 minutes.It features an auto-shut off function that prevents overcooking and a cool touch handle. Perfect for roasting or baking your favorite vegetables and frozen foods, this is a must have air cooker fryer.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 25, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Small but effective
reviews.reviewText: There are only 2 of us and I wanted a small machine for our small kitchen. This works great! Easy to use and easy to clean. I bought paper liners but don’t really think I needed them. Basket is very non-stick. If you want to cook more than 1-2 small portions at a time, get a bigger machine as this has a heating compartment that’s only about 5” square…..not roomy, but good quality. I’m happy with this purchase.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Convenient and useful
reviews.reviewText: I have this to my wife for her birthday after I watched a lot of videos on airfryers and decided that this small enough to fit on the counter, but big enough to be useful for the two of us. My wife was skeptical about using using it, but after learning all the things you can make in it, it's earned a permanent spot on the counter. In the last 4 months we have used it around 3 or 4 times per week. It's easy to use and to wash. Foods come out really good and fast. People said to spray olive oil on foods, but after trying it, I've found most food comes out better without any oil. This little fryer is a great addition to our kitchen and I'd highly recommend it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 15, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Good Machine, Small Footprint
reviews.reviewText: Solid air fryer. Good power, basket is a nice size, compared to the overall size of the unit, affordable. Not much else to say.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 16, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Good product for price
reviews.reviewText: Food comes out really delicious. The size is not big but it’s enough for two people. It’s easy to use and easy to clean. I like the design and works quite. Good price and happy with the purchase

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars It’s so cute!
reviews.reviewText: I bought this for cooking small batches of things for my child who is a bit picky, it’s incredibly silent, absolutely could not hear it, it works fast and is super easy to clean, one of my favorite parts about it is that it’s portable! It has a top handle and the first opportunity I get I will take it to a hotel, I’m glad I got it because I couldn’t find anything larger for the watts and so far I REALLY like it

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 4, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great Price and a Great Little Air Fryer!
reviews.reviewText: This air fryer could not be easier to use and clean! I do recommend using liners -- so your clean-up is reduced to a simple rinse and wipe. Tonight I did fried chicken -- 4 chicken thigs (skin on and bone in) and they came out juicy, tender, and CRISPY after 26 minutes (13 on each side at 400). Bacon is a breeze too; 400 for 7-8 minutes! Everything I've cooked in it has turned out great! Get One!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 29, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars very quiet, easy to use, beautiful color
reviews.reviewText: Very quiet, lightweight, and easy to use. Integrated top handle makes it easy to lift and move. Simple controls. Small basket is adequate for one meal at a time. Beautiful color.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Great gadget for carnivore dieters
reviews.reviewText: This little machine consistently puts out hamburger patties quickly and cooked to perfection, even from a frozen state. It also does very well with 4 to 6 ounce sirloin steaks (not frozen). The trick is to let the meat rest for a minute or two before eating. The machine is quiet, easy to use and easy to clean. It helps me keep on track with my carnivore diet.
Mi mejor aliada en la cocina -AMO-

reviews.reviewTitle: Works! If you shake the contents!
reviews.reviewText: Got it at a great price used - like new. First time I turned it on, it made a terrible grinding sound after 5 mins. Stopped it, took it apart, tightened all the screws inside and voilà! Works like a charm! Things get knocked around in shipping… I need a small model that fit under my 12 inch high cupboards. This fits. It’s small, out of the way, sleek looking with the digital display and so easy to use/fast cooking. I just wished the capacity was better but I understand why it’s not. 5 stars for me.
Papas fritas, hash browns de Sam's Club...Yum! Esta cosa ha cambiado mi vida.
I love this, it works great, easy to use and perfect size for myself and my daughter

I’m really happy with this air fryer. It doesn’t have a lot of bells and whistles but it does the job. The basket is on the smaller side so if you cook for a family you should get something bigger. The colour is very pretty and suits my decor much better than basic black.
